OL,6,FAn accused sword attacker allegedly
OL,7,Fran up behind a 14-year-old boy before
OL,8,Fslashing him in the neck and chest, a
OL,9,Fcourt has heard.JMarcus Arduini Monzo,
OL,10,Fa dual Spanish-Brazilian national
OL,11,Fliving in Newham, east London, is
OL,12,Faccused of murdering teenager Daniel
OL,13,FAnjorin as he was walking to school on
OL,14,FTuesday, and injuring four other
OL,15,Fpeople.JThe 36-year-old appeared at
OL,16,FWestminster Magistrates' Court on
OL,17,FThursday, wearing a grey sweatshirt
OL,18,Fand grey tracksuit bottoms, and
OL,19,Fholding his left arm across his chest.
OL,20,FHe spoke slowly with long pauses to
OL,21,Fconfirm his name in the dock at
OL,22,FWestminster Magistrates' Court.JIt is
OL,23,Falleged that Monzo crashed a van into
OL,24,Fa fence in Laing Close just before 7am
OL,25,Fon Tuesday, hitting a member of the
OL,26,Fpublic.
