OL,6,FThe court was told that he then got
OL,7,Fout of the van, said that he would
OL,8,Fkill the man and slashed him to the
OL,9,Fneck.JProsecutor David Burns told the
OL,10,Fcourt that 15 minutes later it is
OL,11,Falleged Monzo broke into a nearby home
OL,12,Fwhere a couple were asleep with their
OL,13,Ffour-year-old daughter.JHe went into
OL,14,Fthe bedroom and attacked the child's
OL,15,Ffather, shouting about believing in
OL,16,FGod and causing injuries to his neck
OL,17,Fand arm, it is alleged.JMonzo is
OL,18,Faccused of then running up behind
OL,19,FDaniel and attacking him.
